{"tid":2018483,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"翻牆上Twitter的中國人，侮辱我們文宣手足「真TM噁心」「污染了#ACAC」","createTime":"2020-05-15T15:45:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T03:54:02.000Z","uid":48040,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"228caa8ae6e99686a3bbd2e386094e666a9b5f7f","tid":2018483,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T15:45:47.000Z","msg":"<ins>咩係#ACAC？</ins><br />\n話說一班中國的業餘漫畫創作者（有D人自稱藝術家，是但啦），以前係微博上面發布自己的作品，但可能覺得微博尺度唔夠大（即係太性感的圖唔得，會被ban），所以轉戰Twitter，使用#ACAC，即係A Chinese Artist Catalog（應該係，有錯請指正） 。<br />\n然後文宣手足都使用呢個tag，向呢班翻牆出來的人宣傳抗爭運動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Wud9JH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Wud9JH.png&h=13c5c240&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<ins>想要Twitter微博化？</ins><br />\n但呢班中國畫師中，有一部分做慣奴隸，聲言用#ACAC的手足污染了這個tag。佢地希望的是，twitter好似微博咁，有政治審查。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vwHOYAR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvwHOYAR.jpg&h=68a054ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大佬，自己翻牆上twitter，但居然要求twitter的用戶要跟返中國的習慣，不談政治，限制自由。咁到底佢地翻牆上twitter的用意是什麼？純粹為了睇18禁的動漫圖？<br />\n<br />\n=============================<br />\n黃Channel Follower嚴重不足，懇請支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_OtH-ee5lSw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_OtH-ee5lSw&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexofz11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=894772a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_OtH-ee5lSw</a>"},{"pid":"0bbc9dbf9413526028bbc200b8d1f7e253154544","tid":2018483,"uid":247032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T15:52:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0398456c67ab06aa68d55b129fa45c7580058211","tid":2018483,"uid":234695,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T15:58:15.000Z","msg":"10個用vpn嘅中國人有9個都係為咗睇咸野"},{"pid":"d3bca2bf7e045c99476f536935940ee7d77e9484","tid":2018483,"uid":162535,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T17:11:13.000Z","msg":"呢次翻牆出黎大部分係活在自己世界入面果類「歲